{"tid":656770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議院今個禮拜將有對中國貿易法案 (Fair Trade With China Enforcement Act)","createTime":"2018-05-07T13:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T01:32:04.000Z","uid":35790,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dcaadc056a2cc2e708de8d070f256ad4b86e0d1c","tid":656770,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"&lt;轉貼 膠登&gt;<br />\n<br />\n【天下圍攻】美國參議院今個禮拜會再有法案圍攻支那<br />\n<br />\nMarco Rubio (佢見過Gphone哥) 呢個星期會喺參議院推法案圍攻支那<br />\n法案叫 Fair Trade With China Enforcement Act （支那公平貿易推行法）<br />\n<br />\n1. BAM 所有敏感科技唔賣俾支那<br />\n2. 支那人持股美國企業有上限<br />\n3. 美國政府唔准買或租用中興或華為電訊產品（已經提出咗）<br />\n4. 更改1984年支那入息稅條約 - 支那人或法團喺美國投資賺咗錢要交稅 - 呢招係防支那將冥幣貶值 影響美國出口<br />\n5. 對支那製造2025 計劃嘅貨品收稅 同時鼓勵美國盟友咁做<br />\n6. 對跨國企業進入支那搞合營公司額外收稅<br />\nTargeting China&rsquo;s tools of aggression<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/targeting-chinas-tools-of-aggression/2018/05/02/e8446cdc-4e3d-11e8-b725-92c89fe3ca4c_story.html?utm_term=.d26742c9b8a6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2Ftargeting-chinas-tools-of-aggression%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2Fe8446cdc-4e3d-11e8-b725-92c89fe3ca4c_story.html%3Futm_term%3D.d26742c9b8a6&d=smGWapF1gBtCZO2bCLKnjgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6c58c4ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/targeting-chinas-tools-of-aggression/2018/05/02/e8446cdc-4e3d-11e8-b725-92c89fe3ca4c_story.html?utm_term=.d26742c9b8a6</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkgalden.com/view/471830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkgalden.com%2Fview%2F471830&d=smGWapF1gBtCZO2bCLKnjgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b5c56743\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkgalden.com/view/471830</a>"},{"pid":"0abdc426bb9fbed05b2bbbb0906197b3eb1b1847","tid":656770,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c